# Public URL of the Expo Web Dashboard (the app that hosts the real login page).
# The landing page's "Sign in" button navigates here. This is NOT a secret:
# any VITE_ variable is bundled into the public client. Never put passwords,
# JWT secrets, or API keys in a VITE_ variable.
#
# The dashboard is pinned to port 5180 (Expofrontend/expo-web-dashboard
# vite.config.js) so it never collides with expo-mobile-app, which uses the
# default Vite port 5173. The dashboard serves its Login screen at the root URL.
VITE_WEB_APP_URL=http://localhost:5180
